<h3>Adventures</h3>

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-3">
            <h4>Setup</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Ball: -1 coin</li>
                <li>Bridge Troll: -1 coin</li>
                <li>Borrow: -1 card</li>
                <li>Estate: Inheritance</li>
                <li>Ferry: -2 cost</li>
                <li>Giant: journey</li>
                <li>Lost Arts: +1 action</li>
                <li>Pathfinding: +1 card</li>
                <li>Peasant: all +X tokens</li>
                <li>Pilgrimage: journey</li>
                <li>Plan: trashing</li>
                <li>Raid: -1 card</li>
                <li>Ranger: journey</li>
                <li>Relic: -1 card</li>
                <li>Seaway: +1 buy</li>
                <li>Training: +1 coin</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-9">
            <h4>Tavern</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Tan-colored Reserve cards</li>
                <li>When playing a Reserve card, execute above-the-line text</li>
                <li>Card sits on Tavern until it can be called, then execute below-the-line text</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Tokens</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Still function on empty piles</li>
                <li>Can be placed on empty piles</li>
                <li>A pile can have multiple tokens</li>
                <li>+1 action/buy/card/coin bonus when <i>playing</i> that card</li>
                <li>Trashing: may trash a card from hand when <i>buying</i> (not gaining) that card</li>
                <li>-1 card: next time player would draw, draw 1 card less and discard token</li>
                <li>-1 coin: next time player would get at least $1 (from any source), get -1 coin and discard token</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



