<!-- Empires -->
<h3>Empires</h3>

<h4>Debt</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Remove debt during buy phase, after playing treasures</li>
    <li>Debt can be paid down before or after buying cards</li>
    <li>Removing debt does not use up a Buy</li>
</ul>

