                <li>Fool: Lost in the Woods</li>
                <li>Leprechaun: Wish pile</li>
                <li>Necromancer: 3 zombies in trash</li>
                <li>Secret Cave: Wish pile</li>
                <li>Tormentor: Imp pile</li>
                <li>Vampire: Bat pile</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Night phase</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Action - Buy - Night - Cleanup</li>
                <li>Play any number of night cards</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Boon / Hex</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Shuffle, reveal and apply when necessary</li>
                <li>Discard after applying effect</li>
